{"tid":2167303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警長偷影裙底 上訴被駁回須即時服刑","createTime":"2020-08-21T04:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T04:45:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e78892b59714cfcb36d4d3627b46b7f0835fc756","tid":2167303,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:35:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/GBNGSI4HSVCH7OYM7B7JXMBVPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FGBNGSI4HSVCH7OYM7B7JXMBVPA%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliuxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=46dee036\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200821%2FGBNGSI4HSVCH7OYM7B7JXMBVPA%2F&h=b46c8f6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200821/GBNGSI4HSVCH7OYM7B7JXMBVPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n已婚警長休班期間在油塘大本營商場扶手電梯偷拍女子裙底春光，豈料事主原來是「警嫂」，休班警長當場就擒。涉案警長經審訊後被裁定有違公德罪成，判囚兩個月，早前就定罪及刑期提出上訴，並指警方申請調查其手機的手令內容不合法。高等法院法官今駁回上訴，維持原判，指涉案手令內容清晰，警方亦在發現手令範圍不包括上訴人電話內的記憶卡後，再作申請，沒有侵犯私隱。法官又指上訴人身為警務人員，知法犯法，受罰是咎由自取。"},{"pid":"6d82ac9f7c07071b9e09cf0d3eb31550404e468c","tid":2167303,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ee801ca5b0c0cff1c24ac8c1368a4887091501","tid":2167303,"uid":173599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:36:51.000Z","msg":"法官已犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec10a842ee0deb810ffc6342d8a28043c009fec","tid":2167303,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:36:52.000Z","msg":"一定有古怪"},{"pid":"f8eb2342f01c93319f3c3a05bf18bcbd35ed8963","tid":2167303,"uid":271497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eec10a842ee0deb810ffc6342d8a28043c009fec","tid":2167303,"uid":271497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08